title: Humming
alt: I'm so bad at carrying a tune, those 'find a song by humming its melody' websites throw an HTTP 406 error as soon as I start to hum.
transcript:
[Megan is humming a tune.]
Cueball: Hey.
Cueball: What's that?[Megan is still humming the same tune.]
Cueball: What are you humming?
Cueball: Should I know the tune?
Cueball: ...Hmm...[Cueball gets out his phone and opens up a music recognition program.]
Phone: Identify song
Phone: Recorded
Phone: > Live [beta]Phone: Identifying...[A zoom in on the phone screen. An album cover with a picture of Megan on it.]
Positive match:
Check it out!
By I hacked the audio fingerprint database
Feat. MEEEEEE
Track: We're out of cat food (pick some up?)
